node.text: Although we were told asteroid 2018VP1 had virtually no chance of hitting earth, we couldn’t be sure. We built the Global OREO Vault into the permafrost of Svalbard, Norway with only one purpose: To make sure OREO cookies live on for generations to come.

node.text:
Get your free Twist ‘N #BeKind21 deck and OREO cookie pack while you can! We’re giving away* 2,100 game packs - 1 deck of cards with 1 pack of OREO cookies! Tap to claim!

Swipe right to see the game in action 😉

*Pay $3.00 s/h only. Open to 50 U.S. (DC), 13+. Starts 8/31/21; Ends 9/30/21 or when all 2,100 Rewards are claimed, whichever occurs first. See link in bio for Terms and Conditions.

*Pay $3.00 s/h only. Open to 50 U.S. (DC), 13+. Starts 8/31/21; Ends 9/30/21 or when all 2,100 Rewards are claimed, whichever occurs first. See link in bio for Terms and Conditions.
